The following is an example using messages for leaving and arriving
in the new room.  The ! strip out all min and mout messages that
would have been included, so only the specified strings get sent
to the room.

this_player()->move_player("!"+this_player()->query_cap_name()+ \
" leaves through the 'Dionysus' door.", AREA_MYTHOS_ROOM_DIR+ \
"temple_1", "!"+this_player()->query_cap_name()+" steps out \
 of the shadows.");

